  clientBrief: "I manage a mid-sized tech company, and morale is slipping. People
    are overworked, some feel excluded, and I\u2019m worried we\u2019ll lose good
    employees if we don\u2019t fix things soon. What steps should we take to improve
    our workplace culture?"
  choices:
  - choiceText: Offer flexible hours and the option to work remotely.
    reflection: Supports work-life balance and helps prevent burnout.
  - choiceText: Run diversity, equity, and inclusion workshops.
    reflection: Helps employees feel valued and improves team cohesion.
  - choiceText: Launch a wellness program with counseling and fitness perks.
    reflection: Directly addresses stress and supports employee health.
  - choiceText: Start a mentorship program for junior staff.
    reflection: Builds confidence, creates growth opportunities, and strengthens
      loyalty.
  reflectionFeedback: 'Healthy workplaces support people on multiple levels: balance,
    inclusion, wellness, and growth. A mix of these approaches will improve morale
    and reduce turnover.'
